,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T06:28:03.000Z","msg":"台北監獄辦服刑體驗營<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7321/2730142\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7321%2F2730142&d=1evtzUfH0shwkrE1NDTs3C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=5eb86746\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7321/2730142</a>"}]}